    <description>
        <p>kew is a terminal music player with themes and cover-derived colors, lyrics support (.lrc, SYLT, Vorbis comments), MPRIS desktop integration, and support for MP3, FLAC, M4A/AAC, Opus, Ogg, WebM and WAV. It can search and browse your library with gapless playback, playlist editing, and a visualizer. Album art can be shown in sixel-capable terminals via Chafa.</p>
    </description>
    
